    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[60, 60, 501, 199]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 210, 444, 240]]<|/det|>\nஷ்ஷ்யூ5/ Enrolment No.: 0000/98001/21440\nTo\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 240, 342, 351]]<|/det|>\nMadhava Krishna Jetty\nS/O J Naga Bhushanam\nDO NO 44-13/1-1/1A\nKARMI NAGAR\nGUNADALA\nBUDAMERU BRIDGE\nVijayawada (Urban)\nMachavaram\nKrishna Andhra Pradesh - 520004\n8885550848\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[160, 403, 245, 433]]<|/det|>\nSignature Verified\nDate: 2018-12-25\nDate: 2018-12-25\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[375, 416, 475, 479]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 483, 430, 543]]<|/det|>\nஷ்ஷ்யூஸ் / Your Adhaar No. :\n6369\nஷ்ஷ்யூஸ், ஷ்யூஸ்\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[100, 570, 140, 598]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[180, 574, 339, 599]]<|/det|>\nஷ்ஷ்யூஸ்\nGovernment of India\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[70, 606, 161, 678]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[175, 606, 342, 646]]<|/det|>\nMadhava Krishna Jetty\nపుల్స్ శేడి/DOB: 25/11/1986\nపురమ్మడి/ MALE\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[180, 708, 300, 737]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[310, 718, 365, 734]]<|/det|>\n6369\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[145, 740, 386, 755]]<|/det|>\nஷ்ஷ்யூஸ், ஷ்யூஸு\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[375, 681, 465, 737]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[550, 90, 595, 128]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 129, 616, 144]]<|/det|>\nGovernment of India\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[787, 102, 900, 152]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[700, 169, 750, 181]]<|/det|>\nసమాచారం\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[545, 179, 853, 222]]<|/det|>\n■ ఆధార్ కురిపుకు ధృవీకరణ, శాసనతావర్ణి కాదు.\n■ కురిపుకు ధృవీకరణ ఆనందైన ఆఖంబికమైన ద్వారా శాండవస్సు.\n■ ఇది ఎల్లాసిక్ పద్ధతిలో ప్రాయబడిన లేఖ.\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[661, 238, 774, 250]]<|/det|>\n## INFORMATION\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 249, 896, 263]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is a proof of identity, not of citizenship.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 263, 842, 277]]<|/det|>\n■ To establish identity, authenticate online.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 277, 819, 291]]<|/det|>\nThis is electronically generated letter.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 316, 816, 331]]<|/det|>\n■ ఆధార్ దేశమంతటా ఆమోదించబడుతుంది.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 336, 858, 366]]<|/det|>\n■ ఆధార్ భవిష్యత్తులో ప్రభుత్వ మరియు ప్రభుత్వతర సేవలు అందదేయడంలో సహాయ పడుతుంది.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 367, 850, 381]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is valid throughout the country.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 384, 894, 411]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar will be helpful in availing Government and Non-Government services in future.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[600, 576, 857, 601]]<|/det|>\nఖరరఖరవిజ్ఞానరఖరవిజ్ఞానరఖర సంస్థ\nUniquel'dentificationAuthority of India\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[508, 604, 923, 673]]<|/det|>\nAddress:\nS/O J Naga Bhushanam, DO NO 44-13/1-1/1A, KARMIL NAGAR, GUNADALA, BUDAMERU BRIDGE, Vijayawada (Urban), Krishna, Andhra Pradesh - 520004\nఅంత్రమేఖ: 520004\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[640, 705, 750, 737]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[755, 723, 812, 740]]<|/det|>\n6369\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[664, 745, 765, 760]]<|/det|>\nhttps://www.ifad.gov.in\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[360, 789, 737, 920]]<|/det|>\nG. Tadlawala\nJinginji Seo, verified\nEmp Name: D.Kishore\nEmp Code: BG492450\nCompany Name: ABCL Eluru\nSignature: D. K.",
