    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[101, 141, 150, 199]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[365, 149, 480, 201]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 144, 600, 201]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[777, 149, 906, 201]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[171, 209, 410, 241]]<|/det|>\nभारत सरकार\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[675, 223, 725, 238]]<|/det|>\nमाहिती \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 238, 784, 254]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार औलखीचा पुरावा आहे नागरिकत्वाचा नाही \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 252, 848, 282]]<|/det|>\n■ सुरक्षित QR कोड / ऑफलाइन XML / ऑनलाइन प्रमाणीकरण वापरून औलख सत्यापित करा. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 283, 812, 300]]<|/det|>\n■ हे इलेक्ट्रॉनिक प्रक्रिये द्वारा तयार झालेले एक पत्र आहे. \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[101, 277, 457, 313]]<|/det|>\nभारतीय विशिष्ट ओलख प्राधिकरण\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[129, 315, 450, 331]]<|/det|>\nनोंदणी क्रमांक: / Enrolment No.: 1218/61159/05180 \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[140, 334, 170, 348]]<|/det|>\nTo \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[140, 344, 310, 448]]<|/det|>\nशिल्प पंकज मेहता\nShilpa Pankaj Mehta\nW/O: Pankaj Mehta\nFlat No 301, 30 th Floor, Jupiter Apartments\n41 Cuffe Parade\nNear Taj President Hotel\nCuffe Parade\nMumbai\nMumbai Maharashtra - 400005\n9820058625 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[145, 470, 234, 504]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[330, 483, 475, 583]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 590, 465, 608]]<|/det|>\nआपला आधार क्रमांक / Your Aadhaar No. : \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[197, 604, 270, 636]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[197, 622, 377, 638]]<|/det|>\nVID : 9102 0755 7110 8238 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[155, 639, 409, 654]]<|/det|>\nमाझे आधार, माझी ओलख \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[96, 675, 133, 703]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[201, 678, 291, 689]]<|/det|>\nभारत सरकार \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[173, 688, 325, 700]]<|/det|>\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 675, 475, 700]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[99, 714, 120, 771]]<|/det|>\nIssue Date: 05/12/2012 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[111, 707, 210, 789]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 707, 360, 750]]<|/det|>\nशिल्प पंकज मेहता\nShilpa Panka Mehta\nजन्म तारीख/DOB: 07/12/1967\nमहिला/ FEMALE \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 714, 475, 739]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 316, 777, 332]]<|/det|>\nINFORMATION \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 337, 852, 352]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is a proof of identity, not of citizenship. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 351, 916, 380]]<|/det|>\n■ Verify identity using Secure QR Code/ Offline XML/ Online Authentication. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 380, 787, 396]]<|/det|>\n■ This is electronically generated letter. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 425, 694, 440]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार देशभरात वैध आहे \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 440, 819, 468]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार आपल्याला विविध सरकारी आणि खाजगी सेवा सुलभतेने घेण्यास मदत करते \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 468, 820, 494]]<|/det|>\n■ आपला मोबाइल नंबर आणि इमेल आयडी आधारमध्ये अद्यावत ठेवा \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 494, 829, 519]]<|/det|>\n■ आपल्या स्मार्ट फोनमध्ये आधार घ्या - mAadhaar App वापरा \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 534, 835, 551]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is valid throughout the country. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 551, 872, 583]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar helps you avail various Government and non-Government services easily. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 583, 872, 613]]<|/det|>\n■ Keep your mobile number & email ID updated in Aadhaar. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 615, 844, 645]]<|/det|>\n■ Carry Aadhaar in your smart phone - use mAadhaar App. \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[580, 675, 614, 693]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[580, 675, 777, 689]]<|/det|>\nभारतीय विशिष्ट ओलख प्राधिकरण \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[580, 688, 835, 701]]<|/det|>\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 700, 550, 710]]<|/det|>\nपत्ता: \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 708, 728, 750]]<|/det|>\nW/O: पंकज मेहता, फॉर्ट नंबर 301, 30 वा मगल, ज्योतिर आधारेटरन, 41 कफ परेड, शटल ताज शटल जवळ, कफ परेड, मुंबई, मुंबई, महाराष्ट्र - 400005 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 750, 580, 760]]<|/det|>\nAddress: \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[520, 757, 732, 799]]<|/det|>\nW/O: Pankaj Mehta, Flat No 301, 30 th Floor, Jupiter Apartments, 41 Cuffe Parade, Near Taj President Hotel, Cuffe Parade, Mumbai, Mumbai, Maharashtra - 400005 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[750, 714, 900, 814]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[220, 814, 365, 831]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[195, 830, 384, 842]]<|/det|>\nVID : 9102 0755 7110 8238 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[0, 0, 999, 799]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[124, 842, 437, 856]]<|/det|>\nमाझे आधार, माझी ओलख",
