    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[168, 218, 401, 256]]<|/det|>\n## భారత సహర\nGovernment of India\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[102, 295, 465, 335]]<|/det|>\n## భారతీయ విశ్వ ఘరుతు వ్యాధిచార\nUnique Identification Authority of India\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[119, 339, 444, 355]]<|/det|>\n## సిబ్దందణి సెంబ్బి/ Enrollment No.: 0656/33181/03848\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 366, 156, 377]]<|/det|>\nTo\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 377, 230, 390]]<|/det|>\nమొజమ్మడి శిశిందర్\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 392, 231, 404]]<|/det|>\nMohammed Sikander\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 405, 240, 416]]<|/det|>\nS/O Maqbool Hussain,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[138, 416, 199, 427]]<|/det|>\n12/9/175,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 428, 234, 439]]<|/det|>\nnew medarwadi road,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 440, 214, 451]]<|/det|>\nnew medarwadi,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 451, 210, 462]]<|/det|>\nVTC: Raichur,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 463, 201, 474]]<|/det|>\nPO: Raichur,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 475, 219, 485]]<|/det|>\nDistrict: Raichur,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 485, 220, 496]]<|/det|>\nState: Karnataka,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 496, 230, 507]]<|/det|>\nPIN Code: 584101,\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 507, 240, 518]]<|/det|>\nMobile: 9448335793\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[123, 528, 210, 540]]<|/det|>\nSignature valid\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[123, 540, 210, 565]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[320, 527, 470, 629]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[92, 641, 455, 657]]<|/det|>\n## నిమ్మ ఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[186, 659, 377, 688]]<|/det|>\nXXXX XXX 5360\nVID : 9131 0587 2717 0711\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[156, 691, 403, 708]]<|/det|>\nనెన్ను ఆధారం, నెన్ను గురుతు\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[130, 732, 159, 757]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[220, 729, 350, 741]]<|/det|>\n## భారత సహరర\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 743, 360, 755]]<|/det|>\n## Government of India\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[101, 765, 201, 860]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 765, 300, 777]]<|/det|>\nమొజమ్మడి శిశిందర్‌\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 780, 305, 791]]<|/det|>\nMohammed Sikander\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 793, 348, 805]]<|/det|>\nజన్మ దినాంశ/DOB: 01/02/1973\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[208, 807, 280, 819]]<|/det|>\nపురుష/ MALE\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[213, 832, 463, 860]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ\n\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ\n\nఅధారి ఘరుతుని పుణ్యాదేవుణ్ణి, శ్రీరాజు అధిదేవా జన్మ దినాంశదేవి పుణ్యాదేవి\n\nఅల్ల, ఇదేన్ను ఎన్నోని దృఢిశ్రదు అధిదేవా ఠరేణి / ఆఫీల్లన్‌ నమ్మి\n\nనమ్మి, నింగిలండిగి మాత్ర, ఎల్లసిల్ల.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[213, 861, 463, 887]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar is proof of identity, not of citizenship or date of birth. It should be used only with verification (online authentication or scanning of QR code / offline XML)\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[207, 891, 368, 906]]<|/det|>\nXXXX XXX 5360\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[627, 224, 799, 240]]<|/det|>\n## మాటికి / INFORMATION\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 251, 884, 297]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 299, 884, 357]]<|/det|>\nఈ ఆధార పర్తినీదే పురాణయోగిది, శ్రీరాజు అధిదేవా జెన్మ దినాంశదే పురాణ అల్ల.\n'యుజ్ఞిదేవా' వ్యాధిదేవా దీవ్యేయదేవీ నిర్విష్టప్రదేశిరువంతే, నివాసిగృహ\nఒదిగినేదే దాఖలేయ పురాణయనుసారవాగి ఆధారాన్ని జెన్మ దినాంశవేన్ను\nదాఖలేరుగాలిదే.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 359, 738, 372]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁనే\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 374, 884, 409]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ ఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁ\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 411, 884, 434]]<|/det|>\n## వివిధ సౌఖ్యరీ మత్తు సౌఖ్యరీతరే వ్యంజనగళన్ను / సౌఖ్యగళన్ను పడియలు ఆధారో నిమిగి సౌఖ్య మాడుతైది.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 437, 849, 450]]<|/det|>\nనీమ్మ మొబ్బిల్ల సంఖ్య మత్తు ఇమిల్లో బదియన్ను ఆధారోన్ని సేవలరిని.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 452, 856, 465]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁమొజ్ఞన్ను పడియలు మజ్ఞనే ఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁనే ఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁనే\n\n<|ref|>text</td><|det|>[[540, 467, 884, 491]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఊఁఁఁ\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 493, 850, 506]]<|/det|>\nఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁం\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[549, 507, 872, 537]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar is proof of identity, not of citizenship or date of birth (DOB). DOB is based on information supported by proof of DOB document specified in regulations, submitted by Aadhaar number holder.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[549, 539, 876, 587]]<|/det|>\nThis Aadhaar letter should be verified through either online authentication by UIDAI-appointed authentication agency or QR code scanning using mAadhaar or Aadhaar QR Scanner app available in app stores or using secure QR code reader app available on www.uidai.gov.in.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 589, 710, 600]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar is unique and secure.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 601, 860, 622]]<|/det|>\nDocuments to support identity and address should be updated in Aadhaar after every 10 years from date of enrolment for Aadhaar.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 624, 830, 644]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar helps you avail of various Government and Non-Government benefits/services.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 646, 839, 658]]<|/det|>\nKeep your mobile number and email id updated in Aadhaar.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 659, 812, 670]]<|/det|>\nDownload mAdhaar app to avail of Aadhaar services.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 671, 844, 692]]<|/det|>\nUse the feature of Lock/Unlock Aadhaar/biometrics to ensure security when not using Aadhaar/biometrics.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 694, 820, 706]]<|/det|>\nEntities seeking Aadhaar are obligated to seek consent.\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[592, 728, 830, 740]]<|/det|>\n## ఊఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఁఖరీరే\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[591, 740, 833, 753]]<|/det|>\n## Unique Identification Authority of India\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 763, 568, 772]]<|/det|>\nవిశ్వం:\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[515, 770, 740, 800], [516, 805, 557, 815]]<|/det|>\nS/O మేఖలేఖ మేఖనే, ఎం/ఎం/ఎం, నమ్మదేవాడి\nరీళ్ళతో, నేను వ్యవస్థాదేవి, రాయణురే, రాయణురే,\nరాయణురే,\nశనాఖిరే - 584101\nAddress:\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[515, 816, 744, 852]]<|/det|>\nS/O Mapool Hussain, 12/9/175, new madwadi road, new madwadi, Raichur, PO: Raichur, DIST: Raichur,\nKamataka - 584101\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[770, 768, 900, 870]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[631, 877, 800, 890]]<|/det|>\nXXXX XXX 5360\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[633, 892, 799, 904]]<|/det|>\nVID : 9131 0587 2717 0711\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|> satisfying",
