    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[440, 90, 525, 118]]<|/det|>\n## मूचना \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[230, 116, 655, 145]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार पहचान का प्रमाण है, नागरिकता का नहीं । \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[232, 152, 732, 181]]<|/det|>\n■ पहचान का प्रमाण ऑनलाइन प्रमाणीकरण द्वारा प्राप्त करें । \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[395, 284, 596, 308]]<|/det|>\n## INFORMATION \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 305, 737, 334]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is proof of identity, not of citizenship . \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[235, 342, 688, 368]]<|/det|>\n■ To establish identity, authenticate online . \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[231, 475, 508, 501]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार देश भर में मान्य है । \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[232, 509, 696, 562]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार भविष्य में सरकारी और गैर-सरकारी सेवाओं का लाभ उठाने में उपयोगी होगा । \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 561, 680, 589]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is valid throughout the country . \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 597, 748, 647]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar will be helpful in availing Government and Non-Government services in future . \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[250, 714, 333, 754]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[360, 707, 640, 728]]<|/det|>\nभारतीय विशिष्ट भूतवान आधिकरण \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[360, 725, 730, 746]]<|/det|>\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 757, 536, 807]]<|/det|>\nपता: S/O परमानन्द मंधवानी, 34, गोवाल बाग, मानिक बाग रोड, इंदौर, इंदौर जी. पी., मध्य प्रदेश, 452001 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 839, 548, 888]]<|/det|>\nAddress: S/O Parmanand Mandhwani, 34, Gopal Bagh, Manik Bagh Road, Indore, Indore G.P., Madhya Pradesh, 452001 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[570, 763, 758, 899]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[256, 937, 301, 970]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[450, 935, 496, 958]