    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[130, 28, 202, 101]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[360, 42, 675, 103]]<|/det|>\nभारत सरकार\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[70, 113, 290, 337]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[305, 120, 440, 149]]<|/det|>\nरुचि रिप्याठी \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[305, 152, 485, 179]]<|/det|>\nRuby Tripathi \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[300, 186, 688, 216]]<|/det|>\nजन्म दिनांक / DOB : 01/02/1975 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[300, 216, 504, 245]]<|/det|>\nमहिला / Female \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[700, 199, 930, 366]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[528, 351, 655, 387]]<|/det|>\n3615 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[105, 401, 906, 455]]<|/det|>\nआधार - आम आदमी का अधिकार \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[875, 444, 971, 472]]<|/det|>\n15:19 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[71, 540, 225, 618]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[270, 543, 730, 572]]<|/det|>\nमहिला विधि, पदव्यन अधिकारी \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[270, 575, 884, 607]]<|/det|>\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[33, 636, 440, 770]]<|/det|>\nपता: अधिगिनी: पवन रिप्याठी,\nबी-166, पैलेस ओर्फेड, विशाल मेगा\nमट के पास, कौलार रोड, ६जुर,\nभोपाल, कौलार रोड, मध्य प्रदेश,\n462042 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[472, 635, 864, 657]]<|/det|>\nAddress: W/O: Pawan Tripathi, B-166, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[472, 661, 866, 682]]<|/det|>\npalace orchard, near vishal mega mart, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[472, 686, 864, 707]]<|/det|>\nkolar road, Huzur, Bhopal, Kolar Road, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[472, 712, 738, 735]]<|/det|>\nMadhya Pradesh, 462042 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[33, 775, 145, 771]]<|/det|>\n462042 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[513, 846, 630, 878]]<|/det|>\n3615 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[0, 0, 999, 1005]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>i