    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[180, 206, 417, 241]]<|/det|>\n## Government of India\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[135, 280, 485, 316]]<|/det|>\n## Government of India\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[135, 320, 464, 335]]<|/det|>\nनमस्ते कम संज्ञा/ Enrolment No.: 2906/05316/00492\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[150, 342, 275, 483]]<|/det|>\nTo\nఖరు ఖరు ఖరు ఖరు ఖరు ఖరు\nGupta Ankur Shyamprasad\n18,\nTirupati Asian Greenz,\nsadatpura,\nVTC: Sadatpura,\nPO: Sapawada,\nSub District: Idar,\nDistrict: Sabarkantha,\nState: Gujarat,\nPIN Code: 383430,\nMobile: 9998000110\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 500, 220, 533]]<|/det|>\nSignature Not Verified\nDigitally signed by S Unque\nEnrollment Adhaar by India\nDate: 2025/09/19 12:33\nIST\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[345, 495, 483, 590]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[101, 601, 468, 616]]<|/det|>\n## तमारी ज़ाधार नंबर / Your Aadhaar No. :\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[202, 618, 380, 645]]<|/det|>\n7059\nID: 9151 Z2614956 2952\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[163, 649, 415, 665]]<|/det|>\nमारी ज़ाधार, मारी ज़ोलभ\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[101, 682, 130, 711]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[199, 688, 333, 711]]<|/det|>\n## Government of India\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[218, 723, 350, 770]]<|/det|>\nGupta Ankur Shyamprasad\nఖరు తర్వాత/DOB: 19/10/1987\nపురుష/ MALE\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[219, 777, 496, 803]]<|/det|>\nआधार अं शोभननी पुरवो ऐ, नागरिकता अथवा छन तारीफनी नहीं.\nतैनी ऐश्वरो मात्र सरस्वती (श्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीशरीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्र\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[219, 803, 496, 833]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar is proof of identity, not of citizenship or date of birth. It should be used with verification (online authentication, or scanning of QR code / offline XML).\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[304, 841, 351, 857]]<|/det|>\n7059\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[660, 212, 827, 227]]<|/det|>\n## मारिटी / INFORMATION\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 234, 912, 270]]<|/det|>\nआधार अं श्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्रीश्री\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 272, 912, 330]]<|/det|>\nआधार पत्रनीय सरस्वती यु. आई. डी. अ. आई. द्वारा नियुक्त प्रमाणीकरण\nअंशकनी द्वारा अभीवालन प्रमाणीकरण द्वारा अथवा अंशकशन स्टोर पर\nदुबवध अंशमाधार अथवा आधार क्यारस्टर अंश अंशकशननो द्वारा\nकरीने अथवा www.uidai.gov.in पर दुबवध सुरक्षित क्यारस्टर डीडी डेर\nअंशकशननो द्वारा अंशकशन क्यारस्टर डीडी डेर\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 331, 710, 345]]<|/det|>\nआधार अन्य अनेक सुरक्षित छ.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 345, 911, 370]]<|/det|>\nआधार मारे नीचेनी तारीफनी तारीफनी 26 10 वर्ष पड़ी अंगण अनेक सरस्वतीमाने समर्थन आपता ६२तावैजी आधारमा अपडेट थवा छोड़े.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 371, 911, 396]]<|/det|>\nआधार तमने विविध सरस्वती अनेक (विन-सरस्वती बलो/सेवाओने सरस्वतीय मेणववामि मेढ़ ६३ छे.\nआधारमा तमारो मोभाई लंबर अनेक छेमेल आईडी अपडेट रामो.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 397, 864, 411]]<|/det|>\nआधार सेवाओंनी बल भव मारे माMadhaar अंप डाॅनवॉड डरे.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 412, 911, 437]]<|/det|>\nआधार/आधारमे मिट्टिसनो द्वारा पेड़ों ने डरती वापते सुरक्षा सुनिश्चित डरवा मारे आधार ने बंध डर/मोबी/आधारमे मिट्टिसनो सुविधानो द्वारा पेड़ों डरे.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 453, 911, 497]]<|/det|>\nआधार is proof of identity, not of citizenship or date of birth (DOB). DOB is based on information supported by proof of DOB document specified in regulations, submitted by Aadhaar number holder.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 498, 902, 548]]<|/det|>\nThis Aadhaar letter should be verified through either online authentication by UIDAI-appointed authentication agency or QR code scanning using madhaar or Aadhaar QR Scanner app available in app stores or using secure QR code reader app available on www.uidai.gov.in.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 549, 724, 561]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar is unique and secure.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 562, 885, 583]]<|/det|>\nDocuments to support identity and address should be updated in Aadhaar after every 10 years from date of enrolment for Aadhaar.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 584, 850, 605]]<|/det|>\nAadhaar helps you avail of various Government and Non-Government benefits/services.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 606, 860, 618]]<|/det|>\nKeep your mobile number and email id updated in Aadhaar.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 619, 840, 630]]<|/det|>\nDownload madhaar app to avail of Aadhaar services.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 631, 861, 653]]<|/det|>\nUse the feature of Lock/Unlock Aadhaar/biometrics to ensure security when not using Aadhaar/biometrics.\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[560, 654, 840, 666]]<|/det|>\nEntitles seeking Aadhaar are obligated to seek consent.\n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[600, 686, 852, 713]]<|/det|>\n## Government of India\nUnique Identification Authority of India\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[530, 725, 760, 755]]<|/det|>\nसरस्वती :\n18, दोपही अधिकत जीड, सरस्वती, सरस्वती, सरस्वती,\nसरस्वती,\nगुरुत- 383430\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[530, 757, 770, 792]]<|/det|>\nAddress:\n18, Tirupati Asian Greenz, sadatpura, Sadatpura, PO: Sapawada, DIST: Sabarkantha, Gujarat - 383430\n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[777, 727, 920, 823]]<|/det|>\n\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[737, 829, 785, 844]]<|/det|>\n7059\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[655, 844, 810, 856]]<|/det|>\nVID : 9151 2261 4956 2952\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[130, 859, 448, 875]]<|/det|>\nमारे ज़ाधार, मारी ज़ोलभ\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[567, 861, 610, 873]]<|/det|>\n1947\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[660, 861, 920, 875]]<|/det|>\nhelp@uidai.gov.in | www.uidai.gov.in\n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[655, 877, 951, 977]]<|/det|>\nORIGINAL SEEN & VERIFIED\nPLOYEE NAME: MEHUL JOSH\nLOYE CODE: BG188089\nSIGNATURE: N",
