    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 157, 130, 220]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[152, 229, 395, 270]]<|/det|>\nभारत सरकार\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[238, 270, 306, 312]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[91, 312, 456, 351]]<|/det|>\nभारतीय विशिष्ट पहचान प्राधिकरण\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 352, 468, 372]]<|/det|>\nनामांकन क्रम/ Enrolment No.: 1429/70044/00204 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 380, 110, 592]]<|/det|>\nDownload Date: 15/02/2024\nIssue Date: 15/02/2024 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 380, 135, 394]]<|/det|>\nTo \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 394, 205, 410]]<|/det|>\nअग्रवाल विद्याबेन \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 410, 234, 425]]<|/det|>\nAgrawal Vidhyaben \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 424, 300, 439]]<|/det|>\nW/O : Mohanlal, 00, Agarwal \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 437, 300, 452]]<|/det|>\nMohalla, Shitla Chowk, Modi \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 451, 312, 465]]<|/det|>\nvass, Sumerpur, Pali, Rajasthan, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[110, 463, 167, 472]]<|/det|>\n306902 \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[310, 536, 444, 639]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 664, 451, 682]]<|/det|>\nआपका आधार क्रमांक / Your Aadhaar No. : \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[308, 682, 380, 701]]<|/det|>\n2762 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 716, 397, 735]]<|/det|>\nमेरा आधार, मेरी पहचान \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 757, 115, 789]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[180, 760, 260, 771]]<|/det|>\nआरत सरकार \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[160, 771, 300, 785]]<|/det|>\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 757, 469, 782]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[185, 799, 290, 814]]<|/det|>\nअग्रवाल विद्यान \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[185, 812, 320, 828]]<|/det|>\nAgrawal Vidhyaben \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[185, 825, 375, 840]]<|/det|>\nजन्म तिथि / DOB : 01/01/1959 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[185, 839, 304, 854]]<|/det|>\nमहिला / FEMALE \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[78, 799, 197, 878]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 853, 444, 899]]<|/det|>\nIssue Date: 15/02/2024 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[315, 912, 384, 935]]<|/det|>\n2762 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[140, 944, 400, 961]]<|/det|>\nमेरा आधार, मेरी पहचान \n\nimage<|/ref|><|det|>[[0, 0, 999, 964]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[688, 241, 744, 261]]<|/det|>\nसूचना \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 265, 792, 281]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार पहचान का प्रमाण है, नागरिकता का नहीं। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 280, 875, 312]]<|/det|>\n■ सुरक्षित QR कोड / ऑफलाइन XML / ऑनलाइन ऑथेटिकेशन से पहचान प्रमाणित करें। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 312, 814, 330]]<|/det|>\n■ यह एक इलेक्ट्रॉनिक प्रक्रिया द्वारा बना हुआ पत्र है। \n\n<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[650, 351, 777, 368]]<|/det|>\nINFORMATION \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 375, 852, 391]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is a proof of identity, not of citizenship. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 391, 912, 423]]<|/det|>\n■ Verify identity using Smart QR Code/ Offline XML/ Online Authentication. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 424, 781, 440]]<|/det|>\n■ This is electronically generated letter. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 474, 714, 490]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार देश भर में मान्य है। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 490, 802, 522]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार कई सरकारी और गैर सरकारी सेवाओं को पाना आसान बनाता है। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 522, 832, 540]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार में मोबाइल नंबर और इमेल ID अपडेट रखें। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 540, 852, 572]]<|/det|>\n■ आधार को अपने स्मार्ट फोन पर रखें, mAadhaar App के साथ। \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 599, 833, 615]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar is valid throughout the country. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 618, 870, 650]]<|/det|>\n■ Aadhaar helps you avail various Government and non-Government services easily. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 654, 870, 686]]<|/det|>\n■ Keep your mobile number & email ID updated in Aadhaar. \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[536, 689, 841, 722]]<|/det|>\n■ Carry Aadhaar in your smart phone - use mAadhaar App. \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[0, 0, 999, 964]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[771, 757, 920, 789]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 792, 545, 807]]<|/det|>\nपता: \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 805, 748, 848]]<|/det|>\nपत्ती: मोहनलाल, 00, अग्रवाल मोहल्ला, शीतला चौक, मोदी वास, सुमेरपुर, पाली, राजस्थान, 306902 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 851, 576, 864]]<|/det|>\nAddress: \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[509, 863, 737, 900]]<|/det|>\nW/O : Mohanlal, 00, Agarwal Mohalla, Shitla Chowk, Modi vass, Sumerpur, Pali, Rajasthan, 306902 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[749, 913, 816, 935]]<|/det|>\n2762",
