    "ocr_text": "=====================\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 144, 1280])\n=====================\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[89, 152, 140, 199]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[360, 152, 460, 202]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[540, 152, 592, 202]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[758, 145, 888, 195]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[170, 214, 397, 250]]<|/det|>\nஇந்திய அரசாங்கம்\nGovernment of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[100, 288, 465, 330]]<|/det|>\nஇந்திய தனிப்பட்ட அடையாள ஆணைய அமைப்பு\nUnique Identification Authority of India \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[103, 323, 468, 345]]<|/det|>\nபதிலெட்டு எண்/ Enrolment No.: 2192/40694/04463 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 352, 160, 363]]<|/det|>\nTo \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 362, 250, 373]]<|/det|>\nபர்வீன் ஜலாஸ் ஏ \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 373, 219, 383]]<|/det|>\nPerveen Jalal A \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 383, 193, 393]]<|/det|>\nC/O: Jalal, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 393, 170, 403]]<|/det|>\n107, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 404, 260, 415]]<|/det|>\nKanniamman Koil Street, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 415, 220, 425]]<|/det|>\nPeriyanemmel, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 426, 220, 436]]<|/det|>\nVTC: Nemmeli, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 437, 193, 447]]<|/det|>\nPO: Peru, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 447, 285, 458]]<|/det|>\nSub District: Tirukkalkundram, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 458, 245, 469]]<|/det|>\nDistrict: Chengalpattu, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 469, 234, 479]]<|/det|>\nState: Tamil Nadu, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 479, 220, 490]]<|/det|>\nPIN Code: 603104, \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[137, 490, 250, 501]]<|/det|>\nMobile: 8754468588 \n\n<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[130, 508, 222, 519]]<|/det|>\nSignature Not Verified \n\n<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[130, 519, 222, 540]]<|/det|>\n \n\n<|ref|>image<|/re